<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Zando - N°1 des Achats & Ventes en RDC</title>
    <style>
        /* Couleurs de la RDC & Style Général */
        :root {
            --rdc-blue: #007FFF;
            --rdc-yellow: #FCD116;
            --rdc-red: #CE102E;
            --dark: #1A1A1A;
            --light: #F8F9FA;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--light);
            color: var(--dark);
        }

        /* Barre de Navigation */
        header {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px 5%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--rdc-yellow);
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--rdc-blue);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .logo span {
            color: var(--rdc-red);
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--dark);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .btn-publier {
            background-color: var(--rdc-red);
            color: white !important;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-publier:hover {
            background-color: #a00c22;
        }

        /* Section Héro (Grand Titre) */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rdc-blue) 60%, #0056b3);
            color: white;
            padding: 100px 5%;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 40%, var(--rdc-yellow) 40%, var(--rdc-yellow) 43%, var(--rdc-red) 43%, var(--rdc-red) 48%, transparent 48%);
            opacity: 0.15;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .hero .slogan {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--rdc-yellow);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* Barre de recherche grande et claire */
        .search-bar {
            background: white;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            display: flex;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .search-bar input {
            flex: 1;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            outline: none;
        }

        .search-bar button {
            background-color: var(--rdc-blue);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 35px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .search-bar button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        /* Section Catégories */
        .categories {
            padding: 60px 5%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .categories h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .grid-categories {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .card-cat {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .card-cat:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: var(--rdc-blue);
            color: var(--rdc-blue);
        }

        /* Responsive Mobile */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
            .hero .slogan { font-size: 1.5rem; }
            .hero p { font-size: 1.1rem; }
            header { flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; }
            .search-bar { flex-direction: column; border-radius: 20px; padding: 5px; }
            .search-bar button { border-radius: 15px; margin-top: 5px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">🟨 Zando<span>.cd</span></div>
        <nav class="nav-links">
            <a href="#">Accueil</a>
            <a href="#">Annonces</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn-publier">+ Publier une annonce</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>ZANDO</h1>
            <div class="slogan">ACHETEZ. VENDEZ. GAGNEZ.</div>
            <p>La plateforme N°1 des achats et ventes entre particuliers en République Démocratique du Congo.</p>
            
            <div class="search-bar">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Que cherchez-vous aujourd'hui ? (Ex: Toyota RAV4, iPhone...)">
                <button type="button">Rechercher</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="categories">
        <h2>Explorez les catégories</h2>
        <div class="grid-categories">
            <div class="card-cat">🚗 Véhicules</div>
            <div class="card-cat">📱 Téléphones</div>
            <div class="card-cat">🏠 Immobilier</div>
            <div class="card-cat">👕 Mode & Beauté</div>
            <div class="card-cat">🛠️ Services</div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
